*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Include          ZZ0433_ALVGRID_001_F02
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form set_init
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
form set_init .

  gv_title = sy-title.

endform.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form user_command_9000
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
form user_command_9000 .

  save_ok = ok_code.
  clear ok_code.

  case save_ok.
    when `SAVE`.
      perform save_data.
    when ``.
    when others.
  endcase.


endform.

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form save_data
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
form save_data .

  check gt_list is not initial.

  loop at gt_list into data(ls_list).

    append initial line to gt_save assigning field-symbol(<fs_save>).

    <fs_save>-db_key = cl_system_uuid=>if_system_uuid_static~create_uuid_x16( ).

    <fs_save> = corresponding #( base ( <fs_save> ) ls_list ).

  endloop.

  insert zz0433tb1001 from table gt_save.
  if sy-subrc eq 0.
    message |save data ok!| type `S`.
  endif.

endform.
